  <entry>
    <title>服务器有关配置</title>
    <link href="/2022/06/05/vscode%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8B%E8%BF%9E%E6%8E%A5/"/>
    <url>/2022/06/05/vscode%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8B%E8%BF%9E%E6%8E%A5/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="一、vscode远程连接"><a href="#一、vscode远程连接" class="headerlink" title="一、vscode远程连接"></a>一、vscode远程连接</h2><h3 id="1、前述"><a href="#1、前述" class="headerlink" title="1、前述"></a>1、前述</h3><p>在连接到服务器时，在用户目录下的.ssh文件夹中我们能够看到一对公钥与私钥文件</p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/gengjiayao/Image/202207281633391.png" alt="image-20220728163310361" style="zoom: 67%;" /><p>其中，id_rsa为私钥文件，id_rsa.pub为公钥文件</p><p>经过对比，可以发现，id_rsa中的信息与老师所给的文件内容一致</p><h3 id="2、插件下载"><a href="#2、插件下载" class="headerlink" title="2、插件下载"></a>2、插件下载</h3><p>搜索remote，点击下载remote-ssh</p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/gengjiayao/Image/202207281635385.png" alt="image-20220728163508354" style="zoom:50%;" /><h3 id="3、vscode配置"><a href="#3、vscode配置" class="headerlink" title="3、vscode配置"></a>3、vscode配置</h3><p>点击vscode左下角的图标</p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/gengjiayao/Image/202207281635915.png" alt="image-20220728163521890" style="zoom:50%;" /><p>选择第三个选项</p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/gengjiayao/Image/202207281635411.png" alt="image-20220728163532394" style="zoom:50%;" /><p>选择.ssh&#x2F;config，进入配置文件</p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/gengjiayao/Image/202207281635991.png" alt="image-20220728163542965" style="zoom:50%;" /><p>默认文件给出的配置有Host、HostName、User</p><table><thead><tr><th align="center">标签</th><th align="center">解释</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="center">Host</td><td align="center">为此ssh连接命名</td></tr><tr><td align="center">HostName</td><td align="center">ip地址</td></tr><tr><td align="center">User</td><td align="center">用户名</td></tr><tr><td align="center">Port</td><td align="center">端口号，默认为22</td></tr><tr><td align="center">IdentityFile</td><td align="center">验证文件，私钥文件</td></tr></tbody></table><p>例如，在终端里我需要输入以下命令用于连接服务器</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><div class="code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell">ssh -p 23 geng@111.11.11.111 -i ./id_rsa<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>“-p 23”表示为端口号为23；</li><li>“<a href="mailto:&#103;&#x65;&#x6e;&#x67;&#64;&#49;&#49;&#49;&#x2e;&#x31;&#x31;&#46;&#49;&#49;&#46;&#x31;&#49;&#49;">&#103;&#x65;&#x6e;&#x67;&#64;&#49;&#49;&#49;&#x2e;&#x31;&#x31;&#46;&#49;&#49;&#46;&#x31;&#49;&#49;</a>“表示ip地址为111.11.11.111，用户名为geng；</li><li>“-i .&#x2F;id_rsa”表示验证文件为当前目录下的id_rsa文件</li></ul><p>本人根据需要扩充如下</p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/gengjiayao/Image/202207281636183.png" alt="image-20220728163612157" style="zoom:50%;" /><p>保存后，再次点击vscode左下角的图标</p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/gengjiayao/Image/202207281636494.png" alt="image-20220728163625467" style="zoom:50%;" /><p>选择第一个，并选择刚刚命名的BJTU（我这里是BJTU）</p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/gengjiayao/Image/202207281636769.png" alt="image-20220728163637742" style="zoom:50%;" /><p>输入密码，即可成功配置，此时，左下角为此标志。</p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/gengjiayao/Image/202207281636325.png" alt="image-20220728163650297" style="zoom:50%;" />]]></content>
    
    
    
  </entry>
  
  
  
  <entry>
    <title>Hello World</title>
    <link href="/2022/04/28/hello-world/"/>
    <url>/2022/04/28/hello-world/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Welcome to <a href="https://hexo.io/">Hexo</a>! This is your very first post. Check <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/">documentation</a> for more info. If you get any problems when using Hexo, you can find the answer in <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/troubleshooting.html">troubleshooting</a> or you can ask me on <a href="https://github.com/hexojs/hexo/issues">GitHub</a>.</p><h2 id="Quick-Start"><a href="#Quick-Start" class="headerlink" title="Quick Start"></a>Quick Start</h2><h3 id="Create-a-new-post"><a href="#Create-a-new-post" class="headerlink" title="Create a new post"></a>Create a new post</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><div class="code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">$ hexo new <span class="hljs-string">&quot;My New Post&quot;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/writing.html">Writing</a></p><h3 id="Run-server"><a href="#Run-server" class="headerlink" title="Run server"></a>Run server</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">$ hexo server<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/server.html">Server</a></p><h3 id="Generate-static-files"><a href="#Generate-static-files" class="headerlink" title="Generate static files"></a>Generate static files</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">$ hexo generate<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/generating.html">Generating</a></p><h3 id="Deploy-to-remote-sites"><a href="#Deploy-to-remote-sites" class="headerlink" title="Deploy to remote sites"></a>Deploy to remote sites</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">$ hexo deploy<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/one-command-deployment.html">Deployment</a></p>]]></content>
    
    
    
